QuestData.Title: The Warchief Wants You
QuestData.Description: True to his word, Thrall is going to get us going in the right direction to rescue our people. He asked to speak with you.$B$BGood luck, $n. We're all depending on you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Thrall at the Warchief's Lookout on the Lost Isles.
QuestData.RewardText: Once again you have helped us to overcome our mutual enemy, the Alliance.$B$BNow it is time for us to help you.
